#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn3.6"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn3.6:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 3 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 3 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn3.6:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga "
msgstr "1. Shackles "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 6. Appakasutta → appakāsuttaṃ (bj) | appakasuttaṃ (pts2)
msgctxt "sn3.6:0.3"
msgid "6. Appakasutta "
msgstr "6. Few "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.74, pts2ed1.169, sc1
msgctxt "sn3.6:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn3.6:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho rājā pasenadi kosalo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Seated to one side, King Pasenadi said to the Buddha, "

msgctxt "sn3.6:1.3"
msgid "“idha mayhaṃ, bhante, rahogatassa paṭisallīnassa evaṃ cetaso parivitakko udapādi: "
msgstr "“Just now, sir, as I was in private retreat this thought came to mind: "

msgctxt "sn3.6:1.4"
msgid "‘appakā te sattā lokasmiṃ ye uḷāre uḷāre bhoge labhitvā na ceva majjanti, na ca pamajjanti, na ca kāmesu gedhaṃ āpajjanti, na ca sattesu vippaṭipajjanti. "
msgstr "‘Few are the sentient beings in the world who, when they obtain luxury possessions, don’t get indulgent and negligent, giving in to greed for sensual pleasures, and doing the wrong thing by others. "

msgctxt "sn3.6:1.5"
msgid "Atha kho eteva bahutarā sattā lokasmiṃ ye uḷāre uḷāre bhoge labhitvā majjanti ceva pamajjanti, ca kāmesu ca gedhaṃ āpajjanti, sattesu ca vippaṭipajjantī’”ti. "
msgstr "There are many more who, when they obtain luxury possessions, do get indulgent and negligent, giving in to greed for sensual pleasures, and doing the wrong thing by others.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn3.6:2.1"
msgid "“Evametaṃ, mahārāja, evametaṃ, mahārāja. "
msgstr "“That’s so true, great king! That’s so true!” said the Buddha. And he repeated the king’s statement, adding: "

msgctxt "sn3.6:2.2"
msgid "Appakā te, mahārāja, sattā lokasmiṃ, ye uḷāre uḷāre bhoge labhitvā na ceva majjanti, na ca pamajjanti, na ca kāmesu gedhaṃ āpajjanti, na ca sattesu vippaṭipajjanti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn3.6:2.3"
msgid "Atha kho eteva bahutarā sattā lokasmiṃ, ye uḷāre uḷāre bhoge labhitvā majjanti ceva pamajjanti ca kāmesu ca gedhaṃ āpajjanti, sattesu ca vippaṭipajjantī”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn3.6:2.4"
msgid "Idamavoca … pe … "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn3.6:3.1"
msgid "“Sārattā kāmabhogesu, "
msgstr "“Full of desire for possessions and pleasures, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn3.6:3.2"
msgid "giddhā kāmesu mucchitā; "
msgstr "greedy, infatuated by sensual pleasures; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn3.6:3.3"
msgid "Atisāraṃ na bujjhanti, "
msgstr "they don’t notice that they’ve gone too far, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn3.6:3.4"
msgid "migā kūṭaṃva oḍḍitaṃ; "
msgstr "like deer falling into a trap set out. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn3.6:3.5"
msgid "Pacchāsaṃ kaṭukaṃ hoti, "
msgstr "It’ll be bitter later on; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn3.6:3.6"
msgid "vipāko hissa pāpako”ti. "
msgstr "for the result will be bad for them.”"

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
